Well maintained 3 bedroom 2 bath condo available for rent. Conveniently located with close proximity to shops and restaurants. Charters Valley School District. Private primary bedroom with full bath.  Equipped kitchen with nice covered balcony for relaxing. Utilities included in rent (water and gas) with exception of electric which is paid by tenant. Laundry located in basement of building. Quiet neighborhood, plenty of free parking, and nicely landscaped. Quick drive to downtown Pgh and close to major highways. 20 min drive to airport. Good credit rating required. Showings by appointment starting July 30th. Eligible for Scott Township Pool Membership.<br>
